urls.description: While ageing immune systems can make people more susceptible to disease, this is especially true for COVID-19, shingles, influenza and RSV.
urls.title: Age-related decline in immunity: why does it matter and what can be done about it? | GSK

As we age, our immune systems undergo a series of changes that lowers their effectiveness.
